    RowBox[{
    "{", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
     "\"\<## This file is a general .xdc for the NetFPGA SUME Rev. C\n## To \
use it in a project:\n## - uncomment the lines corresponding to used pins\n## \
- rename the used ports (in each line, after get_ports) according to the top \
level signal names in the project\n## Note: DDR, QDR, and GTH Transceiver \
constraints are not included with this document. See applicable reference \n\
##       projects on www.netfpga.org for information on using these \
components\n\n##The following two properties should be set for every design\n\
set_property CFGBVS GND [current_design]\nset_property CONFIG_VOLTAGE 1.8 \
[current_design]\n\n\>\"", "\[IndentingNewLine]", "}"}]}], ";"}], 
